<dl id="n22080g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n22" href="#n22080g">N22 (VI.B.17)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n22all.htm#n22080g"> 80(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> deformed church</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">When he had spoken of good works as necessary for salvation, he had in his mind not Catholicism, but the &ldquo;reformed religion, which is in fact deformed in the extreme.&rdquo; <small> J. Lewis McIntyre, <a name="BRUNO" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#BRUNO"><cite title="source">Giordano Bruno</cite></a> (1903) 80</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
